title: [Guide] How To Use The Poké Ball Plus (Transfer Pokémon, Controls, Etc)
body:
Want to know the many features of the Poké Ball Plus? Feel free to check out our guide #PokeBallPlus #PokemonLetsGo

If you are a proud owner of the Poké Ball Plus, you may already know what you can and can’t do with it. The point of this guide is to help those that are not familiar with its features and show them how to use the Poké Ball Plus. The Poké Ball Plus peripheral can be used as a controller, transfer Pokémon that are inside the ball, train and play with them whilst they are inside. Let’s go over each…
